description:
The crypto provider is currently installed for each domain check in certs.rs:155-156:

```rust
let _ = rustls::crypto::ring::default_provider().install_default();
```

This should be done once at module initialization using `std::sync::Once`:

```rust
use std::sync::Once;
static INIT: Once = Once::new();

fn ensure_crypto_provider() {
    INIT.call_once(|| {
        let _ = rustls::crypto::ring::default_provider().install_default();
    });
}
```

This is a minor optimization but follows best practices.
